title: Cowboys thrash Eagles; Bears QB carousel; Brady returns to New England; Power Rankings
itunes:title: Cowboys thrash Eagles; Bears QB carousel; Brady returns to New England; Power Rankings
description:
In the latest edition of the Good Morning Football Podcast, hosts Kay Adams, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Golden Tate dive into the Dallas Cowboys dominant victory over the Philadelphia Eagles on Monday Night Football. Then they discuss who should be the starting quarterback for the Chicago Bears; Tom Brady's return to New England; and Power Rankings!

The Good Morning Football Podcast is part of the NFL Podcast Network.
